			 			<a href="/f/like/level?kw=%E4%B8%AD%E5%8C%97%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%A6&ie=utf-8&lv_t=lv_nav_intro" target="_blank" class="user_badge d_badge_bright d_badge_icon1" title="本吧头衔1级，经验值0，点击进入等级头衔说明页"><div class="d_badge_title ">寒泉无声</div><div class="d_badge_lv">1</div></a>
